===可视性===
假设这次撞击物是一颗直径约1千米的不活跃彗星或小行星，它的[[视星等|视星等]]将不会亮于25等。<ref name="Hergenrother"/> 而木星的亮度是25等天体亮度的1300亿倍。<ref>([[Apparent_magnitude|5th root of 100]])^(25-(-2.8))=131 billion (1.3E+11)</ref> 大部分小行星巡天探测项目使用广角视场，不能观测到视星等暗于22等（比25等亮16倍）的天体。<ref name="Hergenrother"/> 即使是探测环绕木星公转的10千米以下的木星卫星也是非常困难的，需要世界上最好的望远镜才能做到。<ref name="Sheppard2003">{{cite web |title=New Satellites of Jupiter Discovered in 2003 |publisher=Carnegie Institution (Department of Terrestrial Magnetism) |author=[[Scott_S._Sheppard|Scott S. Sheppard]] |url=http://www.dtm.ciw.edu/users/sheppard/satellites/jup2003.html |accessdate=2009-07-23 |archive-date=2009-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090608233946/http://www.dtm.ciw.edu/users/sheppard/satellites/jup2003.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 直到1999年[[木卫十七|木卫十七]]的发现，天文学家才能发现一些木星的小型卫星。<ref name="moon1999">{{cite web |title=New moon of Jupiter found |publisher=SpaceFlight Now (University of Arizona News Release) |url=http://spaceflightnow.com/news/n0007/21jovianmoon/ |accessdate=2009-07-23 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031020843/https://spaceflightnow.com/news/n0007/21jovianmoon/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

